---
const email = "mike@mikegomez.dev";
const calendly = "https://calendly.com/mike-mikegomez/30min";
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="relative py-32 sm:py-44 bg-void overflow-hidden"
>
  {/* Big ghost type */}
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 -bottom-12 flex justify-center font-display uppercase text-[clamp(180px,30vw,520px)] leading-[0.85] text-gold/[0.1] select-none whitespace-nowrap"
  >
    Let&rsquo;s build
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-14">
    {/* Cinzel inscription opener */}
    <p
      class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-12 reveal tracking-[0.42em] text-[clamp(10px,0.95vw,13px)] uppercase text-clay"
      style="font-family: var(--font-inscription);"
    >
      &mdash; Let&rsquo;s talk &mdash;
    </p>

    <h2
      class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-center font-display uppercase leading-[0.85] text-[clamp(64px,14vw,232px)] tracking-[-0.02em]"
    >
      <span class="block">Let&rsquo;s make</span>
      <span class="block">
        something <span class="text-gold">good</span>
      </span>
      <span class="block text-stroke">together.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-20 sm:mt-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-6">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 md:col-start-4 reveal">
        <p class="text-paper text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 text-center md:text-left">
          Tell me what you&rsquo;re working on, when you&rsquo;d like to
          launch, and the rough budget. Even if it&rsquo;s still just an idea,
          I&rsquo;d love to hear about it. I&rsquo;ll get back within one
          business day, and if we&rsquo;re not the right fit I&rsquo;ll
          gladly point you to someone who is.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a
            href={`mailto:${email}`}
            data-magnetic
            class="group flex items-center justify-between border-t border-iron py-5 hover:border-gold transition will-change-transform"
            data-cursor="hover"
          >
            <span>
              <span class="block font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-smoke mb-1.5">Email</span>
              <span class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-4xl uppercase tracking-[-0.01em] group-hover:text-gold transition-colors break-all">
                {email}
              </span>
            </span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-7 h-7 -rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform flex-shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M5 12 H19 M13 6 L19 12 L13 18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </a>

          <a
            href={calendly}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            data-magnetic
            class="group flex items-center justify-between border-t border-b border-iron py-5 hover:border-gold transition will-change-transform"
            data-cursor="hover"
          >
            <span>
              <span class="block font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-smoke mb-1.5">Calendly</span>
              <span class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-4xl uppercase tracking-[-0.01em] group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">
                Book a 30-min intro call
              </span>
            </span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-7 h-7 -rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform flex-shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M5 12 H19 M13 6 L19 12 L13 18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-10 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-smoke leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left">
          Booking new projects for the next few weeks.<br />
          Most engagements run $3k&ndash;$20k.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
